      "start_time": 6.54,
      "recording_attendee_id": "8b92cea8-e971-4d91-8404-eec00681773a",
      "order_number": 3,
      "text": "Good, good, I just sent you an email like a second ago but I figured I'd give you a call to reason for my call. I saw you had a portfolio in Denver who is using us um a lot of new things going on with uh marketing and advertising with us. You just wanted to try to schedule a nice coffee meeting with you if possible"
