      "start_time": 42.68,
      "recording_attendee_id": "8b92cea8-e971-4d91-8404-eec00681773a",
      "order_number": 13,
      "text": "we uh a bunch of different things but uh main mainly marketing and advertising. Um we have we're our own top ten IOS. We have a lot of unique uh social media products. Um we just launched a new product with google my business and we also have a product that optimizes uh markets market surveys as well. So there's a lot of different things we're doing."
