    {
      "id": "0d829c48-1f54-4016-b695-fa40ce01be27",
      "recording_id": "cde71903-7dc0-4f3c-87cd-cb2770342aeb",
      "end_time": 70.65,
      "start_time": 66.43,
      "recording_attendee_id": "ef87436c-5eb5-475d-acd3-bc5dde855cc9",
      "order_number": 14,
      "text": "Okay. And you said we currently use you um at our in our colorado portfolio?"
    },
    {
      "id": "0d829c48-1f54-4016-b695-fa40ce01be27",
      "recording_id": "cde71903-7dc0-4f3c-87cd-cb2770342aeb",
      "end_time": 80.42,
      "start_time": 70.91,
      "recording_attendee_id": "8b92cea8-e971-4d91-8404-eec00681773a",
      "order_number": 15,
      "text": "Yes. Yeah, I see a regional uses in colorado, the numbers look pretty decent. So I was kind of wondering, you know, you guys are so large, why weren't using"
    },
    {
      "id": "0d829c48-1f54-4016-b695-fa40ce01be27",
      "recording_id": "cde71903-7dc0-4f3c-87cd-cb2770342aeb",
      "end_time": 85.11,
      "start_time": 80.42,
      "recording_attendee_id": "8b92cea8-e971-4d91-8404-eec00681773a",
      "order_number": 16,
      "text": "us in other areas but yes, that's kind of what I wanted to discuss if possible."
    },
    {
      "id": "0d829c48-1f54-4016-b695-fa40ce01be27",
      "recording_id": "cde71903-7dc0-4f3c-87cd-cb2770342aeb",
      "end_time": 109.66,
      "start_time": 86.04,
      "recording_attendee_id": "ef87436c-5eb5-475d-acd3-bc5dde855cc9",
      "order_number": 17,
      "text": "Okay. Um Yeah, I'd be happy to get something on the calendar. Um I would want to include uh the marketing Manager that supports that portfolio and um she's gonna be uh she's gonna be out of the office thursday and friday, so I'm not sure we'll be able to make it work this week but if not we'll we'll put something on the calendar for next week."
    },
    {
      "id": "0d829c48-1f54-4016-b695-fa40ce01be27",
      "recording_id": "cde71903-7dc0-4f3c-87cd-cb2770342aeb",
      "end_time": 114.12,
      "start_time": 110,
      "recording_attendee_id": "8b92cea8-e971-4d91-8404-eec00681773a",
      "order_number": 18,
      "text": "Okay. And you were saying and you were saying the the Denver Marketing Manager?"
    },
    {
      "id": "0d829c48-1f54-4016-b695-fa40ce01be27",
      "recording_id": "cde71903-7dc0-4f3c-87cd-cb2770342aeb",
      "end_time": 115.95,
      "start_time": 114.8,
      "recording_attendee_id": "ef87436c-5eb5-475d-acd3-bc5dde855cc9",
      "order_number": 19,
      "text": "Yes. Mhm."
    },
    {
      "id": "0d829c48-1f54-4016-b695-fa40ce01be27",
      "recording_id": "cde71903-7dc0-4f3c-87cd-cb2770342aeb",
      "end_time": 124.64,
      "start_time": 116.04,
      "recording_attendee_id": "8b92cea8-e971-4d91-8404-eec00681773a",
      "order_number": 20,
      "text": "Okay. I get uh just to get her idea of uh how things are working because I said I wanted to discuss uh the the other portfolios as well."
    },
    {
      "id": "0d829c48-1f54-4016-b695-fa40ce01be27",
      "recording_id": "cde71903-7dc0-4f3c-87cd-cb2770342aeb",
      "end_time": 134.51,
      "start_time": 125.67,
      "recording_attendee_id": "ef87436c-5eb5-475d-acd3-bc5dde855cc9",
      "order_number": 21,
      "text": "Yeah. Yeah, I will um I'll bring her in the loop. Um and uh again we'll just coordinate schedule so we can both jump on a call with you"
    },
