      "start_time": 148.45,
      "recording_attendee_id": "ef87436c-5eb5-475d-acd3-bc5dde855cc9",
      "order_number": 25,
      "text": "Um Alright, let me see. Yeah. Tuesdays are tough because um we we've got a lot of calls as as a team on Tuesday so I would say um Wednesday is the better day but again I had I'd have to look at Ashley schedule as well um you know, because she kind of has her own thing going on also, so um you know, feel free to send it for Tuesday and I'll I'll change it up."
